IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. MEMORY-AND-MOVE.

DATA DIVISION.
01 NUMVAR PICTURE IS 9(3).
01 STRVAR PICTURE IS X(10).
01 TARGET1 PICTURE IS 9(3).
01 TARGET2 PICTURE IS 9(3).

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    DISPLAY "START"
    MOVE 123 TO NUMVAR
    MOVE "HELLO" TO STRVAR
    MOVE 456 TO TARGET1 TARGET2.
